text: Jinsong Road is a street in Pudong New District, Shanghai, People's Republic of China. It is a north-south road, starting from Dingxiang Road in the north, passing through an intersection with Yingchun Road, and ending at Jinxiu Road in the south. == Surrounding buildings == * Shanghai Jincai Experimental Junior Middle School == Intersection Road (from north to south) == * Dingxiang Road * Yingchun Road * Jinxiu Road == Reference == *Facilities near Jinsong Road Category:Streets in Lianyang
